| **Higgs mechanism — gauge boson mass without breaking gauge invariance** | Higgs (1964) *Broken Symmetries and the Masses of Gauge Bosons.* Phys. Rev. Lett. 13, 508 | `10.1103/PhysRevLett.13.508` |
